name: Lilly Ann Winer
bio:
MATHEW WINER DIED MAR 26, 1910 AGED 71 YRS. 9 MOS
HIS WIFE MARY SCHULTZ
DIED JUNE 2, 1911
AGED 72 YRS. 2 MOS
THEIR DAU LILLY ANN
DIED DEC 10, 1901
AGED 20 YRS. 9 MOS
Gone But Not Forgotten
